        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          <a href="/">This Website</a> - A simple website that was made to learn
          <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, which is a cool framework
          that lets you work with parts of React, Preact, Svelte, Vue, SolidJS,
          and more.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Layout>

